  "notes": "Fixed positioning: 1) Start button now positioned absolutely at top:110px, left:120px with transform translate(-50%,-50%) to center it at exactly (120,110). 2) HUD now at top of game-container with padding-top:48px to achieve 48px offset. 3) Legend margin-top:70px places it exactly 70px below the grid bottom. The button is outside game-container to ensure absolute positioning from viewport origin."
}
